params.name: transaction_id
params.description: Transaction id (only for one to one business model)

params.name: is_cancellation_order
params.description: If you mark yes, later will be asked to provide an order id to cancel

params.name: external_reference_id
params.description: External reference id to reference the orders in Adobe system.

params.name: downsize_subscription_id
params.description: Note that downsizing a subscription would mean its auto renewal will be set to false.

params.name: downsize_order_id
params.description: Please note that purchase orders made within the last 14 days can be downsized

params.name: cancel_reason
params.description: Please provide the reason of cancelling the order

params.name: action_type
params.description: Option to customer to choose whether it is a purchase or a transfer

params.name: transfer_id
params.description: Transfer ID of a membership once it it is initiated for transfers

params.name: transaction_items
params.description: Transaction items (number of items within purchase)

params.name: account_creation_date
params.description: The date on which the customer account has been created. Required for transfers.
